{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.1","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:1","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.006.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Arriv\u00e9e d\u2019Esdras \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-28: cf. Esd 8. Ps 119:173.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s ces choses, sous le r\u00e8gne d\u2019Artaxerx\u00e8s, roi de Perse, vint Esdras, fils de Seraja, fils d\u2019Azaria, fils de Hilkija,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.2","name":"Esdras 7:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.6.22","name":"Esdras 6:22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.6.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.2","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:2","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>fils de Schallum, fils de Tsadok, fils d\u2019Achithub,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.3","name":"Esdras 7:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.1","name":"Esdras 7:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.3","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:3","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>fils d\u2019Amaria, fils d\u2019Azaria, fils de Merajoth,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.4","name":"Esdras 7:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.2","name":"Esdras 7:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.4","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:4","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>fils de Zerachja, fils d\u2019Uzzi, fils de Bukki,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.5","name":"Esdras 7:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.3","name":"Esdras 7:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.5","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:5","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>fils d\u2019Abischua, fils de Phin\u00e9es, fils d\u2019\u00c9l\u00e9azar, fils d\u2019Aaron, le souverain sacrificateur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.6","name":"Esdras 7:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.4","name":"Esdras 7:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.6","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:6","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Cet Esdras vint de Babylone: c\u2019\u00e9tait un scribe vers\u00e9 dans la loi de Mo\u00efse, donn\u00e9e par l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Et comme la main de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, son Dieu, \u00e9tait sur lui, le roi lui accorda tout ce qu\u2019il avait demand\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.7","name":"Esdras 7:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.5","name":"Esdras 7:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.7","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:7","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Plusieurs des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, des sacrificateurs et des L\u00e9vites, des chantres, des portiers, et des N\u00e9thiniens, vinrent aussi \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, la septi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e du roi Artaxerx\u00e8s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.8","name":"Esdras 7:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.6","name":"Esdras 7:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.8","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:8","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Esdras arriva \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem au cinqui\u00e8me mois de la septi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e du roi;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.9","name":"Esdras 7:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.7","name":"Esdras 7:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.9","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:9","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>il \u00e9tait parti de Babylone le premier jour du premier mois, et il arriva \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem le premier jour du cinqui\u00e8me mois, la bonne main de son Dieu \u00e9tant sur lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.10","name":"Esdras 7:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.8","name":"Esdras 7:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.10","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:10","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Car Esdras avait appliqu\u00e9 son c\u0153ur \u00e0 \u00e9tudier et \u00e0 mettre en pratique la loi de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et \u00e0 enseigner au milieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl les lois et les ordonnances.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.11","name":"Esdras 7:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.9","name":"Esdras 7:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.11","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:11","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Voici la copie de la lettre donn\u00e9e par le roi Artaxerx\u00e8s \u00e0 Esdras, sacrificateur et scribe, enseignant les commandements et les lois de l\u2019\u00c9ternel concernant Isra\u00ebl:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.12","name":"Esdras 7:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.10","name":"Esdras 7:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.12","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:12","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Artaxerx\u00e8s, roi des rois, \u00e0 Esdras, sacrificateur et scribe, vers\u00e9 dans la loi du Dieu des cieux, etc.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.13","name":"Esdras 7:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.11","name":"Esdras 7:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.13","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:13","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup><span class=\"it\">J\u2019ai donn\u00e9 ordre de laisser aller tous ceux du peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, de ses sacrificateurs et de ses L\u00e9vites, qui se trouvent dans mon royaume, et qui sont dispos\u00e9s \u00e0 partir avec toi pour J\u00e9rusalem.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.14","name":"Esdras 7:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.12","name":"Esdras 7:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.14","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:14","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Tu es envoy\u00e9 par le roi et ses sept conseillers pour inspecter Juda et J\u00e9rusalem d\u2019apr\u00e8s la loi de ton Dieu, laquelle est entre tes mains,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.15","name":"Esdras 7:15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.13","name":"Esdras 7:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.15","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:15","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup><span class=\"it\">et pour porter<\/span><span class=\"it\">l\u2019argent et l\u2019or que le roi et ses conseillers ont g\u00e9n\u00e9reusement offerts au Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, dont la demeure est \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.16","name":"Esdras 7:16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.14","name":"Esdras 7:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.16","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:16","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup><span class=\"it\">tout l\u2019argent et l\u2019or que tu trouveras dans toute la province de Babylone, et les dons volontaires faits par le peuple et les sacrificateurs pour la maison de leur Dieu \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.17","name":"Esdras 7:17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.15","name":"Esdras 7:15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.17","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:17","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup><span class=\"it\">En cons\u00e9quence, tu auras soin d\u2019acheter avec cet argent des taureaux, des b\u00e9liers, des agneaux, et ce qui est n\u00e9cessaire pour les offrandes et les libations, et tu les offriras sur l\u2019autel de la maison de votre Dieu \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.18","name":"Esdras 7:18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.16","name":"Esdras 7:16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.18","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:18","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Vous ferez avec le reste de l\u2019argent et de l\u2019or ce que vous jugerez bon de faire, toi et tes fr\u00e8res, en vous conformant \u00e0 la volont\u00e9 de votre Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.19","name":"Esdras 7:19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.17","name":"Esdras 7:17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.19","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:19","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup><span class=\"it\">D\u00e9pose devant le Dieu de J\u00e9rusalem les ustensiles qui te sont remis pour le service de la maison de ton Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.20","name":"Esdras 7:20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.18","name":"Esdras 7:18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.20","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:20","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Tu tireras de la maison des tr\u00e9sors du roi ce qu\u2019il faudra pour les autres d\u00e9penses que tu auras \u00e0 faire concernant la maison de ton Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.21","name":"Esdras 7:21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.19","name":"Esdras 7:19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.21","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:21","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Moi, le roi Artaxerx\u00e8s, je donne l\u2019ordre \u00e0 tous les tr\u00e9soriers de l\u2019autre c\u00f4t\u00e9 du fleuve de livrer exactement \u00e0 Esdras, sacrificateur et scribe, vers\u00e9 dans la loi du Dieu des cieux, tout ce qu\u2019il vous demandera,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.22","name":"Esdras 7:22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.20","name":"Esdras 7:20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.22","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:22","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup><span class=\"it\">jusqu\u2019\u00e0 cent talents d\u2019argent, cent cors de froment, cent baths de vin, cent baths d\u2019huile, et du sel \u00e0 discr\u00e9tion.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.23","name":"Esdras 7:23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.21","name":"Esdras 7:21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.23","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:23","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Que tout ce qui est ordonn\u00e9 par le Dieu des cieux se fasse ponctuellement pour la maison du Dieu des cieux, afin que sa col\u00e8re ne soit pas sur le royaume, sur le roi et sur ses fils.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.24","name":"Esdras 7:24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.22","name":"Esdras 7:22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.24","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:24","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Nous vous faisons savoir qu\u2019il ne peut \u00eatre lev\u00e9 ni tribut, ni imp\u00f4t, ni droit de passage, sur aucun des sacrificateurs, des L\u00e9vites, des chantres, des portiers, des N\u00e9thiniens, et des serviteurs de cette maison de Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.25","name":"Esdras 7:25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.23","name":"Esdras 7:23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.25","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:25","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Et toi, Esdras, selon la sagesse de Dieu que tu poss\u00e8des, \u00e9tablis des juges et des magistrats qui rendent la justice \u00e0 tout le peuple de l\u2019autre c\u00f4t\u00e9 du fleuve, \u00e0 tous ceux qui connaissent les lois de ton Dieu; et fais-les conna\u00eetre \u00e0 ceux qui ne les connaissent pas.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.26","name":"Esdras 7:26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.24","name":"Esdras 7:24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.26","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:26","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup><span class=\"it\">Quiconque n\u2019observera pas ponctuellement la loi de ton Dieu et la loi du roi sera condamn\u00e9 \u00e0 la mort, au bannissement, \u00e0 une amende, ou \u00e0 la prison.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.27","name":"Esdras 7:27","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.25","name":"Esdras 7:25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.27","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:27","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.007.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>B\u00e9ni soit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de nos p\u00e8res, qui a dispos\u00e9 le c\u0153ur du roi \u00e0 glorifier ainsi la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.28","name":"Esdras 7:28","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.26","name":"Esdras 7:26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.28","label":"","reference":"Esdras 7:28","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.007.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.008.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.7.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>et qui m\u2019a rendu l\u2019objet de la bienveillance du roi, de ses conseillers, et de tous ses puissants chefs! Fortifi\u00e9 par la main de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, mon Dieu, qui \u00e9tait sur moi, j\u2019ai rassembl\u00e9 les chefs d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, afin qu\u2019ils partissent avec moi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7","name":"Esdras 7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.8.1","name":"Esdras 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.8.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.7.27","name":"Esdras 7:27","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.7.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc18c27d6.68010056');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc18c27d6.68010056\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc18c27d6.68010056","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc18c27d6.68010056'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc18c27d6.68010056\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}